Package: sdl-gamecontrollerdb
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: community-sourced SDL game controller mapping database
 This package provides gamecontrollerdb.txt, a community-maintained
 database of controller mappings for SDL2 and SDL3 applications.
 It installs the canonical database in /usr/share/sdl-gamecontrollerdb/
 and also provides a compatibility symlink in /usr/games/.
